(12, '适合发微信朋友圈的经典说说', '18', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">1.听说，世界上最美的相遇是擦肩，最美的誓言是谎言，最美的爱都在昨天，最美的思念是永不相见。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">2.时间会告诉我们，简单的喜欢最长远，平凡中的陪伴最心安，懂你的人最温暖。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3978319643,576191736&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=54F03AD4E141475F0E082857030010F2"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">3.低头不是认输，是要看清自己走的路。仰头不是骄傲，是要看见自己的天空。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">4.若是有缘，时间空间都不是距离；若是无缘，终日相聚也无法会意。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=10254592,4264169732&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=2A1046845AB7D1CC40B27C43030070FA"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">5.做人，要快乐，要开朗，要坚韧，要温暖，要真诚，对生活永远充满希望，微笑面对困境与磨难。多看书看好书。少吃点吃好点。要有梦想，即使遥远。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">6.人生本来就是一场即兴演出，没有做不成的梦，只有不早醒的人。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2471095489,1451674264&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=63B27CC8D226CB4D02A6B011030000DD"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">7.伤口不管有多重，总有痊愈的一天。但遗憾不一样，它会跟随你直到生命终结。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">8.不要害怕改变，尽管你可能会因此失去一些好的东西，但你也可能会得到一些更好的东西。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=215237039,841621426&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=1DA4FC15C941575D4A9D31CF030010E0"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">9.人生不易，且行且珍惜。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">10.生命的真谛不在于呼吸的次数，而是那些令你无法呼吸的时刻。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3366293852,1378832402&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=625&s=3382DC4DC452D3C45A8CBDF203004091"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">11.很多时候别人对你不好，并非因为你不好，而是因为你太好了。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">12.有些人仅仅只是我们生命中一个过客，来无痕去无迹；有些人有缘相守一辈子，却在心里激不起一丝波澜，寡淡无味；有些人仅仅就看了一眼，却在心底从此生根，甚至牵念一生。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2300396694,582496425&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=D99A2BD1CA4367575094044B0300E0D5"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">13.淡淡的相思，眼知道；深深的眷恋，心知道。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">14.没有人可以左右你的人生，只是很多时候我们需要多一些勇气，去坚定自己的选择。别对生活要求太多，生活才会充满惊喜。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=4229710998,2958512862&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=D1933ED14311647542B4086C03009072"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">15.有些记忆，华丽的不敢触碰，却又总是抵挡不住那种诱惑。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">16.时间分割成对角，停止你对我的好，瓦解我们的依靠。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2891457572,255209457&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=BDB0EB15DA1E624D021D2DE303007022"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">17.人只要不失去方向，就不会失去自己！重要的不是所站的位置，而是所朝的方向。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">18.愿时光能缓，愿故人不散；愿你惦念的人能和你道晚安，愿你独闯的日子里不觉得孤单。</span></p><p><img class="large" src="https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2602987645,3801341205&fm=173&app=25&f=JPEG?w=640&h=640&s=7189BC554A42514DDC20807303004023"/></p><p style="margin-top: 26px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">19.人生最大的错误，是用健康换取身外之物；人生最大的悲哀，就是用生命换取个人烦恼。在顺境中感恩，在逆境中依旧心存喜乐，认真活在当下，真实地活在今天。<span class="bjh-br"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="bjh-p">20.有时我们近视，忽略了亲情；有时我们远视，错过了爱情。</span></p><p><br/></p>', 1545377408);
