(19, '唯美的句子大全【500句】', '18', '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1，你说我的眼睛灿若星辰，那是因为你是星辰，而我的眼中只有你。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2，温暖的夏日，一杯香浓的咖啡，一份美味的冰淇淋，青春就是这么甜美。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3，站在青春的夕阳下，感受着过往，留下浅浅的笑靥，这大概就是我们的狂欢过得青春。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="唯美" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181221/1545377491128475.jpg" width="400" height="249"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4，用迷离的舞步，跟随着最后一丝月光的脚步。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5，烟花过后，空气中都充斥着一种浓浓的味道，证明它曾经灿烂过。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6，巴黎铁塔，见证多少情人的分离</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">7，音乐是灵魂寄宿的天堂，人向往的光明。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">8，掩埋了泪眼的斑驳，在转角之后扣上故事门锁</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">9，大海之于小溪，阳光之于地球，蓝天之于白云，棉花糖之于小朋友，美梦之于你，你之于我。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">10，我喜欢那些闪光的东西，比如冬日的雪花，天上的星星，还有你的眼睛。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">11，一个人的生活就像童话，只是没有王子，我也不是公主</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">12，春阳灿灿，夏山如碧，秋蜩抱朴，冬日烈烈，皆愿与君长相随。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">13，看天空的云，堆在了一起。看躺在地上的你，微笑的脸庞。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">14，快乐很简单，就是春天的鲜花，夏天的绿荫，秋天的野果，冬天的漫天飞雪。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">15，想找个保鲜盒把你给我的那些感动都装起来当我不那么喜欢你的时候就拿出来回味一下</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">16，无数的花瓣轻轻摇曳，积攒着彩虹般的梦，承载着我的<a href="http://www.xuejuzi.cn/sinian/32455.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;">思念</a>。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">17，你是我心上一棵万年青</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">18，友谊和花香一样，还是淡一点的比较好，越淡的香气越使人依恋，也越能持久。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">19，勇敢的不是我，是因爲你溫暖了我的手。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">20，像华丽的燕尾蝶，失去往日的光彩、变作一片枯死的叶。旋转，飞扬、最后，深陷于龌龊的沼泽。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="唯美" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181221/1545377491564576.jpg" width="400" height="225"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">21，往事不必再提，<a href="http://www.xuejuzi.cn/renshengganwu/32450.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;">人生</a>已多风雨，我只愿风止于秋水，而我止于你。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">22，你说你要给我蒙娜丽莎的微笑，那你就要对我绽放微笑。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">23，妳的眼睛在閃光燈下折射璀璨的光，唯壹想到的詞是流光溢彩。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">24，看见石头凌空而起，形成一道彩虹般弧线。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">25，他的微笑百看不腻，像阳光柔和干净。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">26，人生是花，而爱是花蜜</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">27，问花花不语为谁开为谁落怨春色三分半随流水、半随尘埃。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">28，最美好的时光，是为一个人付出一切时的勇敢。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">29，我有一个秘密花园，里面装着那些年，我和你的记忆。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">30，想变成太阳花，永远对着太阳笑。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">31，青春在微笑中如花绽放※。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">32，如果我说我要环游世界我可不可以围着你转一圈</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">33，糖的滋味，甜蜜而温暖。所有美好的一切。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">34，无处不在的假象与幻想，梦想一边成长一边灭亡</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">35，心底最柔软的阳光、来自于你孩子般的模样</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">36，刚切开的西瓜，是初恋的颜色。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">37，阳光在每个裂缝中散落。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">38，愿你身畔有一人，始终小心护住你的孩子气，爱着你，像深巷传来酒香，闻之即醉。~</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">39，我遁着岁月的足迹，走过散落一地的旖旎，寻找流年深处的一季花雨。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">40，想变成仲夏夜的一只萤火虫，只要抓住你的注意力，就已经满足了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="唯美" src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181221/1545377492967053.jpg" width="400" height="267"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">41，距离从不会分开两颗真正在乎彼此的心。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">42，流星，只献给我们最美的那一刹那。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">43，牵手一份<a href="http://www.xuejuzi.cn/shuoshuo/32364.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none;">爱情</a>，渴望相伴一生、不离不弃</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">44，你我情如白雪，永远不染尘。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">45，我们依然是彼此天空中最亮的那颗星星//</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">46，时间是外在的光斑，还是心跳微妙的浮点。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">47，最浪漫的事非“左手牵你、右手写爱”莫属</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">48，在角落唱沙哑的歌，再大声也都是给你，请用心听，不要说话。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">49，安静地阅读一本书，嘴角带着静如止水的笑。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">50，青春如此华美，却在烟火在散场</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">51，你的眼睛像一颗恒星撑着黑夜照亮我的生命</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">52，繁花的凋零之是爲了襯托曾經的美好。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">53，以梦喂马，驰骋岁月；以梦为马，诗酒趁年华。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">54，转身的那一刹那，泪，撒了一地。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">55，灯光，继续闪耀。烟花，继续绽放。音乐，继续回响。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">56，一个人走在安安静静的小路上享受夕阳的暖光照耀</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">57，都说你眼中开倾世桃花，却如何一夕桃花雨下。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">58，那些一个人的漫漫时光如影像般定格在年少的底片上</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial; white-space: normal; background-color: r